description: Walking around a shopping centre I met Lukas. His car battery died and he had to replace it. He was fresh out of driving school so he was quite unsure about what to do. I´m far from being a car mechanic but I definitely had more experience than this handsome boy. I offered him my help and together we managed to repair his car. Lukas was very upset by the unexpected expenses caused by the unfortunate situation. He was very attractive so I wanted to help him a little. He looked surprised by my offers. But at the same time he actually looked flattered. He even kept asking me if I found him attractive! What a cute boy. I brought along a lot of money today so I didn´t have to hold back. It was relatively easy to convince him to have some fun on the back seats of his car.
title: Czech Hunter 287
